{
  "stem": "26983.13",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You take it out, and then you throw it back again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, about the people who came back from the camps and such.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The circumstances in Israel were very, very severe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People just had to overcome and build a new life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were so many of the survivors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everyone had it not so easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But of course, for children who had nobody and wanted to study, it was even worse.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We starved, even here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Houser, who was at that time--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hausner.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wanted to know-- they prepared the trial according to all kinds of, let's say, Theresienstadt, deportation, Eichmann, cannibalism.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could give some very useful information on these points.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they called me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I showed them some of my drawings.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They wanted to know how many children are left, let's say, from the last photo of our class of our school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had told them that only very few are alive today, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And because of my good memory, I was later, as I told you, called also for the Eichmann trial, and once for some technical things against another SS man.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And later on, it was very painful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I had all the drawings from the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I knew very well, and there are even statements about what happened not only to me, but other of our group and also in the gas chambers, and described it, groups and single one, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one professor who is quite well known in Israel, Bauer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, oh, these are fantasies of children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody could go to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
